message: "It is critical those looking to harm children in Genesee County know they could very well wind up on the next photo line-up, and have their lives, careers, and families forever impacted. The trauma these predators inflict on their victims is unimaginable, and the consequences for their actions must be severe," Pickell's post said."

data.description: A former Tuscola County Sheriff's deputy is just one among 12 suspects arrested in an ongoing human trafficking investigation, Genesee County Sheriff Robert Pickell announced on Friday.
data.title: Genesee County Sheriff details 12 arrested by human trafficking task force
